    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an investment-grade example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L inline-six remains internally stock, breathing through factory individual throttle bodies with the signature metallic rasp. The Getrag 6-speed manual offers crisp engagement, paired with a refreshed variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system has been bulletproofed with Beisan components. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping, and the chassis remains incredibly rigid. No rod bearing issues; recent Blackstone oil analysis available. This is a turn-key, concours-level driver's car with flawless paint depth and a pristine interior.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
