    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, preserved by a professional ceramic coating and consistent climate-controlled storage. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather seats remain supple, showing no signs of creasing or bolster wear. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive folder of documented dealership service records. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful, offering a collector-grade experience for the most discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
