    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won't believe how beautiful this ride is\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, always kept it in the garage and pampered it. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car smell. If you're looking for something that's practically perfect, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, I'm sure you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
