    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presented is a collector-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS timing. This example is mechanically pristine, with the powertrain delivering a linear power band through a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. All critical preventative maintenance has been documented, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, retaining its original suspension geometry and factory-spec bushings for uncompromising turn-in precision. The exterior retains its factory luster with consistent paint depth across all panels, while the cabin shows no bolster wear or electronic pixel failure. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
